&lt;p&gt;Named #9 on &lsquo;Canada&amp;#8217;s 100 Best Restaurants Award 2015&rsquo;, Chef David Lee has created a regional menu, rich in flavor and inspired by the seasons and multi-ethnic in its influences. The polished setting featuring wood floors, white walls and contemporary art, has a cool downtown vibe and sophisticated elegance. Smart casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a href=&quot;http://notabenerestaurant.com/reservations/&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact Nota Bene via telephone phone at +1 416-977-6400 or via email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@notabenerestaurant.com&quot;&gt;info@notabenerestaurant.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
